oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Photograph of Capt. Eugene Jackson, CSA
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Capt. Eugene Jackson, Co. G, 29th Tenn. Inf. Regt., CSA, of Jonesborough, Tenn. was a graduate of Virginia Military Institute, served under General Stonewall Jackson, and was killed at Murfreesboro, Tenn. He was the son of Brig. Gen. Alfred Eugene Jackson. This photograph was included in a family album.
